<p>Announced a long time ago, the "Cité Internationale du Cinéma d'Animation" should open in 2025 in Annecy.<br>
Screening room, artist residency, exhibitions... a project supported by Annecy Festival, which aims to be like the French Cinematheque of animation.<br>
